{"id":231133860,"title":"Dcard變比原本難用的功能","content":"http://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.png\n\n1.原本網頁版Dcard，「熱門」、「最新」會同時出現，直接點選就能切換，現在變成按一下才能選擇切換，變成比原本多按一下，且每次選擇完下次進來時預設又會跳回「熱門」，session不會自動記錄下來前一次user的選擇。\n\n2.網頁版Dcard如果看到某篇文章想要回應留言，當回完留言後要回到上一頁繼續接著往下看，就只能從上面文章重新開始往下滑，無法從我剛剛點擊的那篇文章接著繼續往下看，很難用超級麻煩。建議可以增加新的變數紀錄點擊文章的SN碼並儲存於session裡，就能改善這個難用又麻煩的問題。","excerpt":"1.原本網頁版Dcard，「熱門」、「最新」會同時出現，直接點選就能切換，現在變成按一下才能選擇切換，變成比原本多按一下，且每次選擇完下次進來時預設又會跳回「熱門」，session不會自動記錄下來前一次user的選擇。","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"0c7337db-20ae-43d8-a310-9b22d6ba5f9d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-04-21T05:59:32.345Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-22T11:35:02.869Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["Dcard","Dcard新功能","bug","問題","狄卡"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{},"forumName":"建議回饋","forumAlias":"dcard","school":"台北海洋科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f325931f-9050-4f64-b318-dbce0468d023","url":"https://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-21T05:59:32.345Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-22T11:35:02.869Z"},{"id":"f325931f-9050-4f64-b318-dbce0468d023","url":"http://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.png","normalizedUrl":"http://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.png","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/qCPLTaV.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-04-21T05:59:32.345Z","updatedAt":"2019-04-22T11:35:02.869Z"}],"postAvatar":""}